{{Youmay|the drug|[[Slick (disambiguation)|other meanings for Slick]]}}
'''Slick''' was a recreational drug that was made from fermented seaweed oil that otherwise had medicinal properties. The primary effect of the drug was that it induced a temporary state of euphoric delirium. The drug originating from the [[Outer Rim Territories/Legends|Outer Rim]] [[Planet/Legends|world]] of [[Vaynai/Legends|Vaynai]]; the [[Bothan/Legends|Bothan]] [[Oneron Fil'vye]], who ran a shipping business that operated out of [[Straysel Island]] on that planet, was a heavy trafficker of Slick.

